doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="IE=edge")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title Parallax Template - Materialize
    link(href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons", rel="stylesheet")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/styles.min.css")
  body
    // Navigation
    nav
      div.nav-wrapper.container
        a(href="#").brand-logo Logo
        a(href="#", data-activates="nav-mobile").button-collapse
          i.material-icons menu
        ul.right.hide-on-med-and-down
          li
            a(href="#") Navbar Link
        ul.side-nav#nav-mobile
          li
            a(href="#") Navbar Link

    // Parallax image
    section.parallax-container
      div.section
        div.container
          div.row.center
            h1 Parallax Template
          div.row.center
            h5.white-text A modern responsive front-end framework based on Material Design
          div.row.center
            a(href="#").btn-large.waves-effect.waves-light Get started
        div.parallax
          img(src="img/background1.jpg", alt="background1")

    // Feauters
    div.section
      div.container
        div.row
          div.col.s4
            div.card-block
              h2.center
                i.material-icons.large flash_on
              h4.center Speeds up development
              p We did most of the heavy lifting for you to provide a default stylings that incorporate our custom components. Additionally, we refined animations and transitions to provide a smoother experience for developers.
          div.col.s4
            div.card-block
              h2.center
                i.material-icons.large group
              h4.center User Experience Focused
              p By utilizing elements and principles of Material Design, we were able to create a framework that incorporates components and animations that provide more feedback to users. Additionally, a single underlying responsive system across all platforms allow for a more unified user experience.
          div.col.s4
            div.card-block
              h2.center
                i.material-icons.large settings
              h4.center Easy to work with
              p We have provided detailed documentation as well as specific code examples to help new users get started. We are also always open to feedback and can answer any questions a user may have about Materialize.

    // Parallax image
    section.parallax-container
      div.section
        div.container
          div.row.center
            h5.white-text A modern responsive front-end framework based on Material Design
      div.parallax
        img(src="img/background2.jpg", alt="background2")

